<subSubSection lastPageId="17" lastPageNumber="468" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1437,474,1147]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,834,859]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466">Description</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[352,413,834,859]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466">Male</emphasis>
. Body length 3.0– 
<quantity box="[624,713,835,859]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.2" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" unit="mm" value="3.2">3.2 mm</quantity>
; wing length 
<quantity box="[867,1006,835,859]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.199999999999999" metricValueMax="4.3" metricValueMin="4.1" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" unit="mm" value="4.199999999999999" valueMax="4.3" valueMin="4.1">4.1–4.3 mm</quantity>
. Head black. Occiput with dense grey pollinosity; with 
<number box="[342,356,871,895]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" value="1.0">1</number>
pair of black verticals; upper part of occiput with numerous moderately long, black bristly hairs above and longer whitish hairs below. Ocellar tubercle with greyish pollinosity, with long anterior and minute posterior setae. Frons narrow, widened before ocellar tubercle, greyish pollinose. Face nearly as broad as frons, slightly widening below, dense silver-grey pollinosity; clypeus with small triangular patch of silver pollinosity above otherwise shiny. Antenna brown to black (sometimes basal segments slightly paler); postpedicel conical, covered with numerous minute setulae, about twice as long as wide; stylus black, 
<number box="[1099,1133,1050,1075]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" value="1.5">1.5</number>
X longer than postpedicel. Gena narrow, shiny. Proboscis dark brown, about 
<number box="[719,733,1086,1111]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" value="2.0">2</number>
/ 
<number box="[741,753,1086,1111]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" value="3.0">3</number>
rds as long as head height. Palpus brown, rather large, oval, whitish pubescent, apically with 
<number box="[519,561,1123,1147]" pageId="15" pageNumber="466" value="2.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.0">2–3</number>
whitish long bristly hairs.
</paragraph>
